@EricZhu0510 The repository is for PowerShell Core. Do you see the issue with latest PowerShell 7.1 RC build?

For Windows PowerShell you should use other resources like UserVoice site, forums and so on. If it is Azure VM issue you could open case in Azure support.
Windows PowerShell is frozen (only security fixes is accepted), all new development continues for PowerShell Core only.
